title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2020
summary: This graph illustrates the Total United States States vehicles to the entering in 2020 .
The Number of cars entering is about 1510198.09 at the start of the year .
It increases towards fall There is a peak at 2339189.19 in August .
gold: The graph shows total United States vehicles entering Canada in 2020 every month . The maximum vehicles recorded entering were in the month of Feb . There was a sharp decline in the number of vehicles entering from Feb to Apr .
